      "id": "629c4cf5a74b9a0023e3a20f",
      "text": "『現代思想入門』",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1654410490,
      "updated": 1774262577
    },
    {
      "id": "629c4d1079e113000084776c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/2a326ffa912399f90b923661eedceb9e]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1654410512,
      "updated": 1774262657
    },
    {
      "id": "69c1196c00000000009873a7",
      "text": "[『現代思想入門』（千葉 雅也）｜講談社 https://www.kodansha.co.jp/book/products/0000363613]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262635,
      "updated": 1774262637
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a200000000009873ad",
      "text": "著:[千葉雅也]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262689,
      "updated": 1774262689
    },
    {
      "id": "629c4d2979e113000084776d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1654410537,
      "updated": 1654410537
    },
    {
      "id": "629c4cf779e113000084776a",
      "text": "[/blu3mo-public/現代思想入門]に読書メモを書いている[blu3mo.icon]",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1654410490,
      "updated": 1654410516
    },
    {
      "id": "629c4cf779e113000084776b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1654410490,
      "updated": 1654410490
    },
    {
      "id": "629c53ea5e90c00000dbcd09",
      "text": "> 《「新書大賞2023」大賞受賞！！》",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1654412265,
      "updated": 1774262694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873af",
      "text": "> 人生を変える哲学が、ここにある――。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b0",
      "text": "> [現代思想]の真髄をかつてない仕方で書き尽くした、究極の「入門書」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262730
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119c200000000009873c5",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262721,
      "updated": 1774262721
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b1",
      "text": "> ■デリダ、ドゥルーズ、フーコー、ラカン、[メイヤスー]……",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262845
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b2",
      "text": "> 最高峰の哲学者たちの「考えていること」が面白いほどよくわかる！",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b3",
      "text": "> ■「物事を[二項対立]で捉えない」「[すべての仕事を“ついで”にやる]」……",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262770
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b4",
      "text": "> 哲学とライフハックがダイレクトにつながる！",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b5",
      "text": "> ■[きちんとしすぎ]る窮屈な管理社会……",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262777
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b6",
      "text": "> [秩序からの逸脱]を肯定する言葉に励まされる！",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262784
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119c400000000009873c6",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262723,
      "updated": 1774262723
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a700000000009873b7",
      "text": "> 「本書は、「こうでなければならない」という枠から外れていくエネルギーを自分に感じ、それゆえこの世界において孤独を感じている人たちに、それを芸術的に展開してみよう、と励ますために書かれたのでしょう。」　――「おわりに　秩序と逸脱」より",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262694,
      "updated": 1774262694
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119a500000000009873ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262693,
      "updated": 1774262693
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b400000000009873b8",
      "text": "> 目次",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262707,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873ba",
      "text": "> はじめに　今なぜ現代思想か",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873bb",
      "text": "> 第一章 [デリダ]――[概念の脱構築]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262830
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873bc",
      "text": "> 第二章 [ドゥルーズ]――[存在の脱構築]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262832
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873bd",
      "text": "> 第三章 [フーコー]――[社会の脱構築]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262834
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873be",
      "text": "> ここまでのまとめ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873bf",
      "text": "> 第四章　現代思想の源流――[ニーチェ]、[フロイト]、[マルクス]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262814
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873c0",
      "text": "> 第五章　[精神分析]と現代思想――[ラカン]、[ルジャンドル]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262827
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873c1",
      "text": "> 第六章　現代思想のつくり方",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873c2",
      "text": "> 第七章　[ポスト・ポスト構造主義]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262821
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873c3",
      "text": "> 付録　現代思想の読み方",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b500000000009873c4",
      "text": "> おわりに　秩序と逸脱",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c119b400000000009873b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774262708,
      "updated": 1774262708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c650840000000000571e9e",
      "text": "#脱構築",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1774604421,
      "updated": 1774604423
